snippet.title: Goodbye Volcano High - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Goodbye Volcano High is a cinematic narrative adventure about the end of an era… and the beginning of a love story. Coming 2021 to PS5, PS4 and PC. 
https://www.goodbyevolcanohigh.com/

Join the discord: http://discord.gg/ko-op

Music: Constellations (Feat. Brigitte Naggar)
Artist: Dabu
Bandcamp: https://dabuaudio.bandcamp.com/track/constellations-ft-brigitte-naggar
YouTube: https://youtu.be/ttatEJNdVY4

A game by KO_OP
https://www.ko-opmode.com/
